.Dd August 4, 2019
.Dt VDSK_SECTOR_SIZE 3
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm vdsk_sector_size
.Nd return the size in bytes of a disk block or sector
.Sh LIBRARY
.Lb libvdsk
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.In vdsk.h
.Ft int
.Fn vdsk_sector_size "vdskctx vdsk"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm vdsk_sector_size
function returns the number of bytes in a disk block, aka sector.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr libvdsk 3 ,
